{
  "stem": "9963.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They got sick, they came down with a-- a cold, put them in the hospital, and many of them didn't come out alive.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Matter of fact, me, you know because I didn't-- I was rubbing my feet got frozen, the toes-- I rub them with the snow, the-- the toes.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But they got frozen anyway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I have still problems with my feet today.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And from our people, what we came to Birkenau Auschwitz, 5,500 plus.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Half were killed right away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The doctor took us to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And from the other half, guess how many people was alive?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We walked out from-- from Birkenau, I mean from Buna Auschwitz, only maybe about a dozen people alive from all that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that number, if you will find a dozen people, that's a lot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where did you sleep when you were in Buna?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, they had barracks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The barracks were the-- very, very good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were also barracks with the bunk beds, but two of them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not the three, just two.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was-- that alone in the Birkenau Auschwitz, was good, because there was enough water to-- to wash up, there was lavatories, and that was OK.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But all of rest of it, was not OK.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The food was not OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The work was too hard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the-- the conditions, they were-- the way that they were treating you is very unhumane.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In Buna-- if we-- if we finished the quarantine, they give us to another barrack, you know, and another work.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When I did work in a factory, what I cut my fingers, and later, when I went to the hospital, or sort of, I cut the fingers-- it was around 1 o'clock in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
